# Project context

This repo is an **external** certificate discovery service — not a Vault secrets-engine plugin.

- **v1:** network TLS scan + PostgreSQL + REST API + Next.js dashboard
- **v1.1:** Vault PKI reconciliation via HTTP API (`internal/vault/` — planned)

Read [docs/architecture.md](../../docs/architecture.md) and [docs/data-model.md](../../docs/data-model.md) before schema or API changes.

Org rules (Superpowers, SDLC, commit policy) live in global `org-*.mdc` or Cursor Team Rules.
